rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0002
rows.name: Stand down, Lin. We've cleared the area.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0003
rows.name:
No further hostile signatures detected.
All enemy craft in the combat arena have been destroyed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0005
rows.name: We did it? We did it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_SEL0011
rows.name: Suggest another wave might hit soon.

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0007
rows.name:
That was way too few troops—
they must be testing our defenses.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0008
rows.name: Ugly aliens got one look at heropon Tatsu and surrendered![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0010
rows.name: Yeah, I'll cook a big feast![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0013
rows.name:
That was way too few troops—
they must be testing our defenses.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0014
rows.name: —absolutely huge, and it's airborne. And coming in fast.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0015
rows.name: The enemy are planning to attack NLA from above![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0016
rows.name:
I knew it—the ground attack was a feint.
Everyone, we need to get back to the city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0019
rows.name:
We tried to avoid it, but now we have no choice.
Better to risk damaging the city than losing it altogether.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08070100_MSG0020
rows.name:
The hostile forces have crossed the perimeter.
They've entered NLA airspace![ST:wait ]
